metadata.name: Pirate Ship
metadata.description:
Somewhere in Neverland, there was an old pirate ship hiding in the middle of the ocean.
A long time ago, a pirate family left their land looking for gold. They were sailing and sailing all around the high seas searching for hidden treasures in the ocean. But the main treasure they gained was their “freedom”. They didn’t belong to any place anymore; they only belonged to themselves.
On their way to find the most valuable treasure, they faced many dangers...! After all, great treasure comes with great cost….!

Edition 1/1
3500 * 4960 px
Hand-drawn on paper, edited in Adobe Photoshop and Adobe Illustrator
